Source: xubuntu-artwork
Section: x11
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Xubuntu Developers <xubuntu-devel@lists.ubuntu.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 7.0.50~)
Standards-Version: 3.9.1
Vcs-Bzr: lp:xubuntu-artwork
Vcs-Browser: http://bazaar.launchpad.net/~xubuntu-art/xubuntu-artwork/maverick/files

Package: xubuntu-artwork
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, gtk2-engines-murrine, murrine-themes (>> 0.98.2),
 libnewt0.52 (>= 0.52.11-2ubuntu7)
Recommends: plymouth-theme-xubuntu-logo, plymouth-theme-xubuntu-text,
 xubuntu-wallpapers, xubuntu-icon-theme
Description: Xubuntu themes and artwork
 This package contains Xubuntu themes and artwork.

Package: xubuntu-wallpapers
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: Xubuntu wallpapers
 This package contains the default wallpapers for Xubuntu.

Package: xubuntu-plymouth-theme
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, plymouth-theme-xubuntu-logo, plymouth-theme-xubuntu-text
Description: Plymouth theme for Xubuntu
 Transitional package for plymouth-theme-xubuntu-logo and
 plymouth-theme-xubuntu-text.
 .
 This package can be safely removed.

Package: plymouth-theme-xubuntu-logo
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, plymouth, plymouth-label
Replaces: xubuntu-plymouth-theme
Provides: plymouth-theme
Description: graphical boot animation and logger - xubuntu-logo theme
 Plymouth is an application that runs very early in the boot process
 (even before the root filesystem is mounted!) that provides a graphical
 boot animation while the boot process happens in the background.
 .
 This package contains the default xubuntu-logo theme.

Package: plymouth-theme-xubuntu-text
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, plymouth, plymouth-theme-ubuntu-text
Provides: plymouth-theme
Description: graphical boot animation and logger - xubuntu-text theme
 Plymouth is an application that runs very early in the boot process
 (even before the root filesystem is mounted!) that provides a graphical
 boot animation while the boot process happens in the background.
 .
 This package contains the default xubuntu-text theme used when no support for
 a graphical theme is found on your system.

Package: xubuntu-icon-theme
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, elementary-icon-theme
Description: Xubuntu icon theme
 This package contains the default icon theme for Xubuntu.
